title: Full Frys
overview: Full Frys is a Swedish situation comedy. Sture Bergholm (Stefan Gerhardsson) is shop manager for the grocery store "Dolkens Livs" in Falkenberg. His five colleagues, not least Edvin Eriksson (Krister Claesson), often pose a lot of problems both for his work and privacy. Sture's girlfriend Evy Karlsson (Annika Andersson) is also his secretary at work.
